lead_paragraph: Gabby Douglas tried to block out the criticism when national team coordinator Martha Karolyi named the reigning Olympic champion to the 2016 gymnastics team last month despite a so-so performance at trials.

headline.print_headline: Olympic Champion Gabby Douglas Eager to Prove Critics Wrong
